        <div class="inner-services">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-truck-medical"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Emergency Services</h3>
          <p>
            Our emergency services are available 24/7 to provide immediate care
            for critical conditions. Our team of emergency medical professionals
            is trained to handle a wide range of emergencies, ensuring that
            patients receive prompt and effective treatment.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="inner-services">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <i class="fa-regular fa-hospital"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Inpatient Care</h3>
          <p>
            Our inpatient care services provide comprehensive treatment and
            support for patients who require hospitalization. We offer
            comfortable accommodations and personalized care plans to ensure a
            smooth recovery process.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="inner-services">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <i class="fa-regular fa-heart"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Outpatient Services</h3>
          <p>
            Our outpatient services include routine check-ups, diagnostic tests,
            and minor procedures that do not require an overnight stay. We
            strive to make our outpatient services convenient and accessible for
            all patients.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="inner-services">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-notes-medical"></i>
